---
title: Puglia-Style Shrimp Orecchiette with Roasted Tomato, Parmesan & Parsley
description: This simple, rustic pasta dish will take you straight to the heel of Italy’s boot–the Puglia region, where this dish is from. It stars burst tomatoes roasted with garlic and panko and a glossy olive-oil rich sauce. You’ll garnish it generously with Parmesan and parsley and there it is–an authentic Italian dinner in a quick 20 minutes–delizioso!
